title: This Is Motorpsycho  -  The movie
description:
- This is Motorpsycho - 

When Motorpsycho left on their third European tour in the spring of 1994, they where joined by friend and fan, filmmaker Kjetil Solhoi. For two weeks he dogged their tails in the tradition of Marty di Bergi and other R`n`R filmmakers- documenting the stupidity, the boredom, the fun and moments of transcendence of a band on the road.
For added spice this 60.min plus video includes promotional videos and exclusive backstage footage.


Ripped from my original VHS.

No subtitles

Enjoy!
